					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You should learn most of the 6502 assembly, as that is the syntax all the assemblers use standardly, the only real features others add are tags and stuff. Look up in the assemblers files for the README or something along those lines to find what it offers and how to access those features like tags and such.</div>

